T1  - Retracted: Risk Management in Financial Institutions
AU  - RAMPINI, ADRIANO A.
AU  - VISWANATHAN, S.
AU  - VUILLEMEY, GUILLAUME
Y1  - 2020/04/01
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2020/04/01
